val spark = org.apache.spark.sql.SparkSession.builder
        .master("local")
        .appName("Spark CSV Reader")
        .getOrCreate;
        
val df_text = spark.read
         .format("csv")
         .option("header", "true") //first line in file has headers
         .option("mode", "DROPMALFORMED")
         .load("/home/user/IdeaProjects/project2/data/nyc-parking-ticket-2014.csv")

df_text.registerTempTable("df")
